name: Individual Transforming 200k
description:
Individual Transforming 200k marble with a seed based on the owner's tezos-address, renders differently for every owner. 
At a certain point in time, this OBJKT will stop displaying vertical lines and transform into something new. Press the 'SPACEBAR' for a hint at when this will happen.

Uses the hicdex API and therefore depends on it. This is all experimental and might break in the future. - @TeNinEightNFTs
